Package: alsa-relay-bridge
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, python3 (>= 3.9), python3-smbus, python3-alsaaudio, i2c-tools
Recommends: alsa-utils
Description: ALSA bridge for Allo RelayAttenuator volume control
 This package provides a daemon that bridges ALSA volume controls
 to the Allo RelayAttenuator hardware via I2C communication.
 .
 Hardware Requirements:
  - Allo BossDAC
  - Allo Relay Attenuator
  - Raspberry Pi with I2C enabled
 .
 The daemon monitors ALSA mixer events and translates volume changes
 to relay attenuator commands, providing hardware-level volume control.
